{"tid":1221041,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"嚟緊星期日(6月16日) 下午二點半 大遊行 維園至政府總部","createTime":"2019-06-14T06:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T03:00:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dedcfc97d8d5245d5ebbd1eb51f042935e7bf38d","tid":1221041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:27:02.000Z","msg":"嚟緊星期日(6月16日) 下午二點半 大遊行 維園至政府總部<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front<br />\n<br />\n【民陣宣佈：星期日大遊行 星期一集會三罷】<br />\n<br />\n昨日（6月12日），有數萬名市民到金鐘政府總部和立法會外集會，力阻立法會審議逃犯條例修訂，成功令立法會大會無法舉行；但警方無情鎮壓，以催淚彈，橡膠子彈和布袋彈傷害平民，民陣對此強烈譴責！<br />\n<br />\n警方竟然使用致命武力，甚至向參與已經批准的集會市民發射催淚彈；而且，警方在大型集會向市民開槍，是回歸以來首見，其傷害性足以令人永久傷殘；林鄭月娥無視警方開槍鎮壓，卻定性集會為暴動，愧為人母，愧為特首！<br />\n<br />\n子彈射進每一個市民心中，香港人痛心疾首。但我們要向全世界說：香港人反惡法，永不放棄！民陣會和所有香港人堅持到底！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">民陣已向警方申請星期日（6月16日）下午二時半舉辦大遊行，由維園到政府總部。遊行訴求只有三點：<br />\n<br />\n一，譴責警方暴力鎮壓市民；<br />\n二，撤回逃犯條例修訂；<br />\n三，林鄭月娥必須下台！</span><br />\n<br />\n同時，民陣已向警方申請星期一（6月17日），在立法會外集會。民陣呼籲全港市民繼續罷課，罷市，罷工，阻止修例通過。<br />\n<br />\n最後，民陣嚴正聲明，倘若政府拒絕撤回修例，所有建制派議員必須順應主流民意，公開表明會投反對票！<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線<br />\n2019年6月13日<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n被捕法律支援熱線：6549 9452<br />\nWhatsapp / SMS / Telegram<br />\n<br />\n被捕者需提供資料：<br />\n1. 中英文姓名<br />\n2. 身份證號碼<br />\n3. 性別<br />\n4. 年齡<br />\n5. 聯絡電話<br />\n6. 緊急聯絡電話<br />\n7. 所在警署<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n民陣已開設 TG 頻道發放資訊：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCivilHumanRightsFront&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=d53883ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62494659_2300277373352974_974281423785558016_n.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=b4952bc63a0aa5bfad7bb6f92e956278&amp;oe=5D9D485B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F62494659_2300277373352974_974281423785558016_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3Db4952bc63a0aa5bfad7bb6f92e956278%26oe%3D5D9D485B&h=b9c900c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2300277366686308/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.517931904920872%2F2300277366686308%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=5b3b374b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2300277366686308/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"70760c2e35c9cac621e6805dd70010faf99d3043","tid":1221041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:56:46.000Z","msg":"後日"},{"pid":"f0b9a7a497956ed503ef498e8bd995a92712dad8","tid":1221041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:37:33.000Z","msg":"大家都推下呢個, <br />\n<br />\n浮唔到面就少人見到,<br />\n<br />\n琴日先決定,  驚有好多人未知."},{"pid":"584d853d3849ed72a9e666d3a6178f30d4843a3f","tid":1221041,"uid":259302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:43:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期日和理非遊行，爭取沉默大多數支持先！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"391e5ec2274ebeff36a6e0c6d9add2c7e0ba0d08","tid":1221041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:04:39.000Z","msg":"後日"},{"pid":"56e378e8af25bad8ebed6a0de66f19e4ed37f6a7","tid":1221041,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:48:56.000Z","msg":"最重要是全家總動員，參與兩大行動！<br />\n<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: orange;\">星期日黑色大遊行</span><br />\n6. 下周一「三罷」總集會<br />\n<br />\n還有任何行動，你想到的，都可以盡量嘗試。<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62601134_2302124196501625_5957941885271015424_n.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=a486aed6f099c66a186e91b5480c14a2&amp;oe=5D93D109\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F62601134_2302124196501625_5957941885271015424_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3Da486aed6f099c66a186e91b5480c14a2%26oe%3D5D93D109&h=8aaa05ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2302124186501626/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.517931904920872%2F2302124186501626%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=2e614128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2302124186501626/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"17c3ca9f16482f9cc5173c4dbb57c6a2968ef15f","tid":1221041,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:02:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9aa2f083edb37975f4291617570d7b49a843913","tid":1221041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:51:21.000Z","msg":"上次白色, 今次黑色衫, 仲唔係佢哋所謂既 顏色革命 ?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa781cc3f714c97ba711103350b9cc99f87f15a0","tid":1221041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:55:46.000Z","msg":"最新消息<br />\n<br />\n譴責鎮壓 撤回惡法 大遊行<br />\n<br />\n日期：6月16日<br />\n時間：下午2時30分<br />\n起點：維多利亞公園*<br />\n終點：金鐘添美道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">民陣呼籲市民穿著黑色衫</span>，譴責警方鎮壓，要求撤回惡法，林鄭月娥下台！<br />\n<br />\n*民陣同時通知警方擬多於一個起點舉辦遊行，明日將和警方進一步商討，請大家留意民陣宣佈。"},{"pid":"45076f7a348c2554961fccc12d06bc2bd74f0d46","tid":1221041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:17:17.000Z","msg":"聽日無變， 繼續維園起步<br />\n<br />\n聽日見"},{"pid":"a02f4039a99537ba062b15242d0c077caf0e182d","tid":1221041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:42:43.000Z","msg":"民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front<br />\n2 小時 &middot; <br />\n(Please see English text below)<br />\n<br />\n民陣轉載：<br />\n<br />\n反送中受傷被捕者人道支援基金<br />\nAnti-Extradition Protest Trust<br />\n<br />\n本基金成立為支援所有因參與早前反送中運動抗議而受傷，被捕的示威者。並由以下社會人士︰吳靄儀、何韻詩、許寶強、何秀蘭擔任臨時信託人。<br />\n<br />\n本基金將於6月16日民間人權陣線遊行期間，收集社會各界對有需要人士的支持。其餘資訊將盡快公佈。<br />\n<br />\n反送中受傷被捕者人道支援基金<br />\n2019年6月15日上午11時37分<br />\n<br />\nAbout the Trust:<br />\n<br />\nThe Trust is established to support protesters who were injured or arrested because of participating in the anti-extradition protests. Margaret Ng Ngoi-yee, Denise Ho Wan-see, Prof. HUI Po-keung and Cyd HO Sau-lan will be the temporary Trustees.<br />\n<br />\nThe Trust needs the support from different sectors in society during the Civil Human Rights Front protest on 16/6. Relevant information will be released as soon as possible.<br />\n<br />\nAnti-Extradition Protest Trust<br />\n15 June 2019 11:37 am<br />\n<br />\n#AntiExtraditionProtestTrust<br />\n#反送中受傷被捕者人道支援基金<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/&hellip;/a.368493197184&hellip;/368493147184189/&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fa.368493197184%E2%80%A6%2F368493147184189%2F%E2%80%A6&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=e3cfeb03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/&hellip;/a.368493197184&hellip;/368493147184189/&hellip;</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/64536556_368493150517522_1688994497582596096_n.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=8c9b5ca7f1a2283050920baf40411755&amp;oe=5D9321CD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F64536556_368493150517522_1688994497582596096_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D8c9b5ca7f1a2283050920baf40411755%26oe%3D5D9321CD&h=00955f0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2 小時 &middot; <br />\n關於基金︰<br />\n<br />\n本基金成立為支援所有因參與早前反送中運動抗議而受傷，被捕的示威者。並由以下社會人士︰吳靄儀、何韻詩、許寶強、何秀蘭擔任臨時信託人。<br />\n<br />\n本基金將於6月16日民陣人權陣線遊行期間，收集社會各界對有需要人士的支持。其餘資訊將盡快公佈。<br />\n<br />\n反送中受傷被捕者人道支援基金<br />\n2019年6月15日上午11時37分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/CivilHumanRightsFront/posts/?ref=page_internal&amp;mt_nav=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fposts%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal%26mt_nav%3D0&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=35ca0148\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/CivilHumanRightsFront/posts/?ref=page_internal&amp;mt_nav=0</a>"},{"pid":"49e657909b13f93cfb69bbeb946eb6baf40ae2e6","tid":1221041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:21:52.000Z","msg":"聽日繼續<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9414acab010ba62ca8490cd6e08f015dd4b6b246","tid":1221041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:49:46.000Z","msg":"今次黑色衫"},{"pid":"854cf1d550471a52ba5c8c00ca0ca4651cf96fc5","tid":1221041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:41:16.000Z","msg":"黑色衫"},{"pid":"a182eb81bfb9c6697e86b71574d8c4e39c18c2a8","tid":1221041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"854cf1d550471a52ba5c8c00ca0ca4651cf96fc5","tid":1221041,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:41:16.000Z","msg":"黑色衫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:00:40.000Z","msg":"黑衫"}]}